pr_body:
Renamed the `set` method to `setValue` to emphasize camel case (and `set` is a syntax error anyway).

I'm not a huge fan of checking in the generated code but it works out of the box.

@abhinav @junchaowu @breerly

@tseaver not sure how I feel about the `NO COVER`'s.  The only other option I could think of was skipping tests on windows.

Appveyor: https://ci.appveyor.com/project/daspecster/gcloud-python-utjkc

LMKWYT

change dict used by run/serve from 

{predictor_name -> archive_file} 
to 
{demo_model_name -> (predictor_name, archive_file)}

which is a better representation and (in particular) allows us to have different demo models that share the same `Predictor` wrapper

(this will allow us to have a single `sentence_tagger` predictor that can be used by the NER model and by (say) a future POS tagger)

* Replace `M2Crypto` with `cryptography` (delegate proxy support).
* Bump SDK to v1.1.1

@ranantha We're going to hold this release pending possibly communication to our existing delegate proxy users about the switch.

@kalefranz 

The URL parsing would swap around locations of URL parts if passed a `/t/<TOKEN>` URL that was not the `channel_alias`.

Patch includes a test that reproduces the problem, and a possible fix.

Closes #237 
Or at least adds a test which breaks.
@arkilic
